'''唇彩'''也稱為'''唇蜜'''，是一种[[化妆品|化妆品]]，主要用于给[[嘴唇|嘴唇]]添加光泽，有时也用于給嘴唇添加一些細微的颜色<ref name="WilliamsSchmitt2012">{{Cite book|last=S.D. Williams|last2=W.H. Schmitt|title=Chemistry and Technology of the Cosmetics and Toiletries Industry|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VW3sCAAAQBAJ&pg=PA149|date=6 December 2012|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-94-009-1555-8|pages=149–|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2020-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207192527/https://books.google.com/books?id=VW3sCAAAQBAJ&pg=PA149|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1930年，{{link-en|蜜丝·佛陀|Max Factor Sr.}}發明了唇彩<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.seeing-stars.com/museums/maxfactor.shtml|title=Max Factor Biography|publisher=The Max Factor Museum|accessdate=2010-09-02|archive-date=2010-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100824200500/http://www.seeing-stars.com/museums/maxfactor.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thebiographychannel.co.uk/biographies/max-factor.html|title=Max Factor Biography|publisher=Biography Channel UK|accessdate=2010-09-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100829070915/http://www.thebiographychannel.co.uk/biographies/max-factor.html|archivedate=2010-08-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。第一款商業化唇彩產品於1932年推出<ref>{{Cite web|title=History of Lip Gloss|url=https://makeup.lovetoknow.com/History_of_Lip_Gloss|author=Sharma|first=Tanya|work=LoveToKnow|accessdate=2021-01-15|archive-date=2019-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904121525/https://makeup.lovetoknow.com/History_of_Lip_Gloss|dead-url=no}}</ref>。唇彩一般是液體，或是較軟的固體。唇彩會有不同層次的透明度，從[[透明|透明]]到完全不透明，而且可以有各種磨光、閃光、光澤的表面<ref name="WilliamsSchmitt2012"/>。

唇彩和醫療用或舒緩用的[[潤唇膏|潤唇膏]]不同，也和顏色較深的口紅不同。

